 <span data-ttu-id="30ced-350">Im folgende C#-Beispiel veranschaulicht die legen Sie die <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.Tombstone%2A> Eigenschaft `true`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30ced-350">The following C# example shows how to set the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.Tombstone%2A> property to `true`.</span></span>  
  
